Enable the following options in the kernel configuration

File systems --->
  <*/M> Btrfs filesystem support                                      [BTRFS_FS]

With LVM2
File systems --->
  <*/M> Btrfs filesystem support                                      [BTRFS_FS]
  [*]     Btrfs POSIX Access Control Lists                  [BTRFS_FS_POSIX_ACL]